536
00:31:21,217 --> 00:31:22,947
<b>Yes, I can spare some time.</b>

537
00:31:23,747 --> 00:31:26,116
<b>Then let's have a chat for once.</b>

538
00:31:33,957 --> 00:31:37,266
<b>When did we first meet?</b>

539
00:31:39,527 --> 00:31:42,637
<b>October 17, 1995.</b>

540
00:31:43,266 --> 00:31:44,866
<b>It was a rainy Tuesday.</b>

541
00:31:45,266 --> 00:31:47,006
<b>When you were young,</b>

542
00:31:47,006 --> 00:31:49,506
