543
00:31:49,946 --> 00:31:52,376
<b>getting locked up in your closet.</b>

544
00:31:52,376 --> 00:31:54,076
<b>Are you still scared of that?</b>

545
00:31:55,476 --> 00:31:59,586
<b>Dad, I'm sorry.</b>

546
00:31:59,586 --> 00:32:03,486
<b>Please open this. Dad.</b>

547
00:32:03,986 --> 00:32:05,057
<b>Lee Jeong Hoon!</b>

548
00:32:05,227 --> 00:32:06,596
<b>Why won't you listen to me?</b>

549
00:32:06,757 --> 00:32:09,826
