550
00:32:10,897 --> 00:32:12,926
<b>Please let me out.</b>

551
00:32:12,926 --> 00:32:13,936
<b>Be quiet!</b>

552
00:32:16,036 --> 00:32:17,266
<b>Dad!</b>

553
00:32:17,867 --> 00:32:21,137
<b>Dad! Dad!</b>

554
00:32:21,137 --> 00:32:22,137
<b>Yes.</b>

555
00:32:22,777 --> 00:32:24,576
<b>I know it's embarrassing, but I am.</b>

556
00:32:28,316 --> 00:32:30,516
<b>What about regarding Seo Yeon?</b>

557
00:32:31,647 --> 00:32:37,126
<b>Are your memories and feelings
about her the same?</b>

558
00:32:51,467 --> 00:32:54,807
<b>The images
are still very vivid to me.</b>

559
00:32:55,337 --> 00:32:56,947
<b>I see.</b>

560
00:32:57,546 --> 00:32:58,947
<b>To be honest,</b>

561
00:32:59,947 --> 00:33:02,816
<b>I was meaning to ask you this
