566
00:33:18,927 --> 00:33:21,536
<b>Yes, it's true.</b>

567
00:33:22,337 --> 00:33:25,237
<b>But you'll never be able
to forget Seo Yeon.</b>

568
00:33:25,906 --> 00:33:30,307
<b>How could you start
a new relationship in that state?</b>

569
00:33:30,506 --> 00:33:31,876
<b>Is it actually possible?</b>

570
00:33:34,147 --> 00:33:37,346
<b>I'm just surprised, that's all.</b>

571
00:33:39,487 --> 00:33:40,617
<b>I'm going to try to work it out.</b>

572
00:33:42,517 --> 00:33:44,686
<b>She's someone dear to me.</b>

573
00:33:46,656 --> 00:33:50,427
<b>I don't want to live
the rest of my life in regret.</b>

574
00:33:52,267 --> 00:33:53,267
<b>Is that so?</b>

575
00:33:54,237 --> 00:33:55,237
<b>All right.</b>

576
00:33:55,666 --> 00:33:59,207
<b>You look happy, so I'm relieved.</b>

577
00:34:01,006 --> 00:34:02,036
<b>I'm glad.</b>

578
00:34:03,006 --> 00:34:04,006
<b>Thank you.</b>

579
00:34:08,747 --> 00:34:10,017
<b>What do you think?</b>

580
00:34:10,017 --> 00:34:15,316
<b>("The Man Who Cannot Forget")</b>

581
00:34:15,316 --> 00:34:16,987
<b>I like this one the best.</b>

582
00:34:17,386 --> 00:34:20,596
<b>Okay, we'll use this.</b>

583
00:34:20,596 --> 00:34:21,596
<b>All right.</b>

584
00:34:22,196 --> 00:34:24,827
<b>How long will it take
