585
00:34:24,827 --> 00:34:27,936
<b>Well, I think I'll need
a few more weeks.</b>

586
00:34:27,936 --> 00:34:29,036
<b>Oh, right.</b>

587
00:34:30,036 --> 00:34:32,307
<b>You wrote about a patient.</b>

588
00:34:32,307 --> 00:34:35,177
<b>The renowned news anchor
