611
00:35:54,017 --> 00:35:57,827
<b>How could you start
a new relationship in that state?</b>

612
00:35:57,827 --> 00:35:59,257
<b>Is it actually possible?</b>

613
00:36:04,627 --> 00:36:05,767
<b>Hey, Tae Eun.</b>

614
00:36:08,067 --> 00:36:09,267
<b>What do you think?</b>

615
00:36:09,267 --> 00:36:12,337
<b>It suits you. Not only will you be
