673
00:38:35,676 --> 00:38:37,947
<b>How will his family manage
if he's put behind bars?</b>

674
00:38:37,947 --> 00:38:40,687
<b>I'm not buying it.
Don't you ever mention him again.</b>

675
00:38:49,827 --> 00:38:52,267
<b>I guess my father called you over.</b>

676
00:38:53,127 --> 00:38:54,166
<b>Yes.</b>

677
00:38:54,967 --> 00:38:58,437
<b>Next time he calls, say no.
You don't have to listen to him.</b>

678
00:38:59,007 --> 00:39:00,337
<b>But I have to listen to you?</b>

679
00:39:01,877 --> 00:39:04,277
<b>No, you don't have
to listen to me either.</b>

680
00:39:04,507 --> 00:39:07,046
<b>When you were young, hypnotherapy,</b>

681
00:39:07,046 --> 00:39:10,217
<b>medication, and counseling may have
helped you, but not anymore.</b>

682
00:39:10,517 --> 00:39:14,587
<b>Your determination
is what put you here.</b>

683
00:39:15,416 --> 00:39:18,527
<b>You need neither my father
nor my help anymore.</b>

684
00:39:18,786 --> 00:39:20,426
<b>So don't listen to us.</b>

685
00:39:21,226 --> 00:39:23,296
<b>There's nothing difficult
about receiving a checkup.</b>

686
00:39:24,596 --> 00:39:26,937
<b>And I'll be forever grateful to him.</b>

687
00:39:27,467 --> 00:39:28,837
<b>That'll never change.</b>

688
00:39:32,337 --> 00:39:34,907
<b>So was the checkup
all that you received?</b>

689
00:39:34,907 --> 00:39:36,337
<b>Did he have any other questions?</b>

690
00:39:37,646 --> 00:39:39,307
<b>He asked about Ha Jin.</b>

691
00:39:41,177 --> 00:39:43,016
<b>He asked if we were serious.</b>

692
00:39:45,287 --> 00:39:47,217
<b>He had asked me
several times before.</b>

693
00:39:48,087 --> 00:39:51,457
<b>I think he's been watching the news.
You don't have to explain it to him.</b>

694
00:39:53,187 --> 00:39:55,596
<b>We are in a serious relationship.</b>

695
00:39:57,896 --> 00:40:00,136
<b>What do you mean?</b>

696
00:40:00,366 --> 00:40:01,537
<b>It's exactly what I said.</b>

697
00:40:03,067 --> 00:40:05,266
<b>Don't you know her condition?</b>

698
00:40:05,407 --> 00:40:07,876
<b>Her memories might come back...</b>

699
00:40:07,876 --> 00:40:10,106
<b>if you remain by her side.</b>

700
00:40:10,447 --> 00:40:12,646
<b>I know. I know that.</b>

701
00:40:14,016 --> 00:40:16,276
<b>But I don't want to shun her
because of that.</b>

702
00:40:17,187 --> 00:40:18,646
<b>Even if her memories come back
and she struggles,</b>

703
00:40:18,646 --> 00:40:20,157
<b>I'm going to be there for her.</b>

704
00:40:24,157 --> 00:40:26,327
<b>I've given this a lot of thought.</b>

705
00:40:29,957 --> 00:40:33,266
<b>Among all the decisions
you've made to this day,</b>

706
00:40:33,896 --> 00:40:36,096
<b>I had never gone against any.</b>

707
00:40:36,866 --> 00:40:39,807
<b>Because you were
a cautious and wise individual.</b>

708
00:40:40,407 --> 00:40:43,577
<b>But not this time.</b>

709
00:40:44,407 --> 00:40:46,177
<b>You don't seem like
the Jeong Hoon I know.</b>

710
00:40:47,376 --> 00:40:49,516
<b>That's because I did change.</b>

711
00:40:51,787 --> 00:40:53,856
<b>I'm not going
to hide in fear anymore.</b>

712
00:41:00,957 --> 00:41:04,766
<b>Doctor, Ms. Oh Mi Young
is waiting for you.</b>

713
00:41:06,327 --> 00:41:08,596
<b>I'll let you go back to work.
I'll call you.</b>

714
00:41:19,006 --> 00:41:23,146
<b>Oh, hi. How's the hangover?</b>

715
00:41:24,717 --> 00:41:27,986
<b>It's fine,
but I don't remember much.</b>

716
00:41:28,587 --> 00:41:30,427
<b>How did I go home?</b>

717
00:41:30,587 --> 00:41:33,256
<b>I carried you home, of course.</b>

718
00:41:33,626 --> 00:41:34,756
<b>Seriously?</b>

719
00:41:35,256 --> 00:41:38,596
<b>How could you have carried me
with that tiny body of yours?</b>

720
00:41:39,967 --> 00:41:43,537
<b>Don't you ever boast
about drinking well, got it?</b>

721
00:41:44,337 --> 00:41:45,407
<b>I'm sorry.</b>

722
00:41:45,967 --> 00:41:48,307
<b>I didn't make any mistakes, did I?</b>

723
00:41:49,707 --> 00:41:51,577
<b>No... No, you didn't.</b>

724
00:41:51,577 --> 00:41:53,646
<b>Really? I'm glad.</b>

725
00:41:54,447 --> 00:41:56,516
<b>Will you be working out today?</b>

726
00:41:57,146 --> 00:41:58,787
<b>Yes, I will.</b>

727
00:41:58,817 --> 00:42:01,187
<b>Then I'll see you
around the same time as yesterday.</b>

728
00:42:01,486 --> 00:42:02,516
<b>All right.</b>

729
00:42:12,866 --> 00:42:14,136
<b>You're so tiny...</b>

730
00:42:14,467 --> 00:42:15,537
<b>and cute.</b>

731
00:42:35,557 --> 00:42:36,787
<b>Why do I keep thinking about her?</b>

732
00:42:38,157 --> 00:42:40,957
<b>I must have had too many drinks.
Goodness.</b>

733
00:42:41,126 --> 00:42:43,256
<b>My entire body aches.</b>

734
00:42:43,866 --> 00:42:45,797
<b>I should ask her
to go easy on me today.</b>

735
00:42:46,496 --> 00:42:48,636
<b>I'm sorry for calling you
all of a sudden like this.</b>

736
00:42:49,236 --> 00:42:53,006
<b>No, it's all right. Actually,
I wanted to get some fresh air.</b>

737
00:42:54,537 --> 00:42:56,876
<b>But I hope everything is okay.</b>

738
00:42:57,846 --> 00:43:00,106
<b>I was just a bit worried.</b>

739
00:43:00,677 --> 00:43:03,376
<b>You recently went through
something traumatic.</b>

740
00:43:03,646 --> 00:43:06,447
<b>I was worried if it took
a psychological toll on you.</b>

741
00:43:06,917 --> 00:43:08,856
<b>And I was wondering
if you needed my help.</b>

742
00:43:09,717 --> 00:43:11,427
<b>I'm okay now.</b>

743
00:43:11,427 --> 00:43:13,157
<b>It's all in the past.</b>

744
00:43:13,856 --> 00:43:15,026
<b>I'm glad to hear that.</b>

745
00:43:15,356 --> 00:43:18,467
<b>Right. If you need help later,
feel free to call me.</b>

746
00:43:19,126 --> 00:43:20,667
<b>Thank you, doctor.</b>

747
00:43:25,037 --> 00:43:29,006
<b>The other day,
we talked about your dream.</b>

748
00:43:29,006 --> 00:43:30,646
<b>You said you had a weird dream.</b>

749
00:43:30,846 --> 00:43:33,177
<b>Did you have a similar dream
like that ever since then?</b>

750
00:43:35,646 --> 00:43:38,287
<b>I did have similar dreams
after the first one.</b>

751
00:43:40,116 --> 00:43:42,157
<b>But I'm really fine these days.</b>

752
00:43:42,557 --> 00:43:45,327
<b>Thanks to Anchor Lee,
I'm really happy.</b>

753
00:43:45,657 --> 00:43:48,126
<b>- I see.
- If you aren't too busy,</b>

754
00:43:48,126 --> 00:43:49,197
<b>we should meet up together.</b>

755
00:43:49,197 --> 00:43:51,297
<b>We can get
something delicious and talk.</b>

756
00:43:51,827 --> 00:43:52,827
<b>Sure.</b>

757
00:44:05,876 --> 00:44:08,116
<b>(First Date, 7:40 a.m.)</b>

758
00:44:14,116 --> 00:44:15,787
<b>Who is it this early in the morning?</b>

759
00:44:17,226 --> 00:44:18,557
<b>It's for me!</b>

760
00:44:18,557 --> 00:44:20,856
<b>It's for me. Don't touch it!</b>

761
00:44:23,096 --> 00:44:26,167
<b>My goodness. What on earth is it?</b>

762
00:44:27,366 --> 00:44:28,837
<b>What did you buy this time?</b>

763
00:44:28,837 --> 00:44:30,167
<b>Some stuff.</b>

764
00:44:30,467 --> 00:44:33,236
<b>I thought you were going
on a date with Anchor Lee today.</b>

765
00:44:33,467 --> 00:44:35,106
<b>You said it was
your official first date.</b>

766
00:44:35,876 --> 00:44:37,146
<b>Yes, that's right.</b>

767
00:44:37,146 --> 00:44:38,776
<b>Can you help me move them?</b>

768
00:44:48,087 --> 00:44:49,516
<b>I decided on my wish.</b>

769
00:44:49,516 --> 00:44:52,386
<b>Today, you have to do
everything I ask you to do.</b>

770
00:44:54,927 --> 00:44:56,197
<b>She's making me anxious.</b>

771
00:44:58,827 --> 00:45:01,496
<b>I'm in front of your house.
Open the door for me.</b>

772
00:45:09,136 --> 00:45:10,677
<b>What's going on?</b>

773
00:45:10,677 --> 00:45:13,047
<b>We were supposed to meet
two hours later.</b>

774
00:45:13,047 --> 00:45:15,246
<b>I need water.
Could you give me a cup of water?</b>

775
00:45:15,246 --> 00:45:17,016
<b>Water? Okay.</b>

776
00:45:24,457 --> 00:45:25,457
<b>Here.</b>

777
00:45:27,457 --> 00:45:29,096
<b>What's all this?</b>

778
00:45:29,856 --> 00:45:31,327
<b>Open them now.</b>

779
00:45:38,266 --> 00:45:39,266
<b>Presents.</b>

780
00:45:39,467 --> 00:45:41,077
<b>They are all yours.</b>

781
00:45:43,606 --> 00:45:45,246
<b>What are...</b>

782
00:45:57,957 --> 00:45:59,827
<b>Don't you think
you'd look great in these?</b>

783
00:45:59,827 --> 00:46:01,557
<b>It's perfect on you. Right?</b>

784
00:46:02,026 --> 00:46:03,356
<b>I'm not sure.</b>

785
00:46:04,197 --> 00:46:05,327
<b>I don't know.</b>

786
00:46:05,327 --> 00:46:07,337
<b>That was made for you.</b>

787
00:46:07,337 --> 00:46:10,967
<b>Put that one. And what else
will look good with that?</b>

788
00:46:12,207 --> 00:46:13,667
<b>And try them with this.</b>

789
00:46:14,876 --> 00:46:16,207
<b>Put them on now?</b>

790
00:46:16,207 --> 00:46:18,606
<b>Yes, it's my wish.</b>

791
00:46:18,907 --> 00:46:22,077
<b>Wait. Have you been hating
my outfits all this time?</b>

792
00:46:22,077 --> 00:46:24,447
<b>You did talk about my tie
when you were on my show.</b>

793
00:46:24,447 --> 00:46:25,986
<b>Are you giving me
a wardrobe makeover?</b>

794
00:46:25,986 --> 00:46:27,616
<b>It's not that.</b>

795
00:46:27,817 --> 00:46:29,687
<b>It's our first date.</b>

796
00:46:29,856 --> 00:46:31,726
<b>There's this place
I really want to go,</b>

797
00:46:31,726 --> 00:46:33,896
<b>but I don't want people
to recognize us.</b>

798
00:46:33,896 --> 00:46:36,226
<b>If you go out dressed like that,
people will spot us in five minutes.</b>

799
00:46:36,226 --> 00:46:37,827
<b>It'll be so easy to recognize you.</b>

800
00:46:37,827 --> 00:46:39,766
<b>Think of this as a type of disguise.</b>

801
00:46:39,766 --> 00:46:41,937
<b>I don't think that will work on me.</b>

802
00:46:41,937 --> 00:46:43,067
<b>Trust me on this.</b>

803
00:46:43,067 --> 00:46:45,537
<b>People won't recognize you at all.
I assure you.</b>

804
00:46:45,537 --> 00:46:48,736
<b>Besides, you're supposed to do
whatever I ask of you today.</b>

805
00:46:51,006 --> 00:46:52,346
<b>Hurry and get changed.</b>

806
00:46:53,917 --> 00:46:55,646
<b>I did have a bad feeling about it.</b>

807
00:47:04,386 --> 00:47:06,126
<b>I really don't think
this is working.</b>

808
00:47:06,957 --> 00:47:08,327
<b>Let's try the next outfit.</b>

809
00:47:16,797 --> 00:47:18,506
<b>Is it supposed to look like this?</b>

810
00:47:26,547 --> 00:47:28,917
<b>What do you say? Do you like it?</b>

811
00:47:30,947 --> 00:47:31,947
<b>The last one.</b>

812
00:47:33,016 --> 00:47:34,687
<b>- Another one?
- It's the last one.</b>

813
00:47:49,766 --> 00:47:51,006
<b>See?</b>

814
00:47:51,006 --> 00:47:53,707
<b>I bet you also think
this color stands out too much.</b>

815
00:47:53,707 --> 00:47:56,876
<b>No, I'm looking at you
because it looks great on you.</b>

816
00:47:57,106 --> 00:47:59,276
<b>From now on,
wear an outfit like this.</b>

817
00:47:59,276 --> 00:48:01,516
<b>It lightens up your looks
and makes you look more dashing.</b>

818
00:48:02,016 --> 00:48:04,217
<b>I really think you're teasing me.</b>

819
00:48:04,417 --> 00:48:06,016
<b>No, I'm not.</b>

820
00:48:06,117 --> 00:48:07,117
<b>By the way,</b>

821
00:48:07,786 --> 00:48:11,026
<b>what is this place
you wanted to go on a date?</b>

822
00:48:11,026 --> 00:48:14,226
<b>Oh, that.
You'll know once we get there.</b>

823
00:48:14,726 --> 00:48:17,296
<b>I daresay
you never thought of this place.</b>

824
00:48:17,967 --> 00:48:20,326
<b>All of a sudden, you're scaring me.</b>

825
00:48:20,897 --> 00:48:23,236
<b>Was going on dates supposed
to be full of thrill like this?</b>

826
00:48:23,236 --> 00:48:24,967
<b>I'm really excited.</b>

827
00:48:37,147 --> 00:48:39,687
<b>Is this the place
you wanted to come on a date?</b>

828
00:48:39,687 --> 00:48:40,687
<b>Yes.</b>

829
00:48:41,717 --> 00:48:43,586
<b>I don't see anything special here.</b>

830
00:48:44,026 --> 00:48:46,526
<b>Isn't the cherry blossom path
just so gorgeous?</b>

831
00:48:46,526 --> 00:48:47,826
<b>Whenever I passed by here in a car,</b>

832
00:48:47,826 --> 00:48:50,256
<b>I saw couples holding hands here.</b>

833
00:48:50,256 --> 00:48:52,066
<b>I was really jealous of them.</b>

834
00:48:55,397 --> 00:48:56,397
<b>What is it?</b>

835
00:48:57,137 --> 00:48:59,236
<b>Were you disappointed
because it's too plain?</b>

836
00:48:59,766 --> 00:49:00,836
<b>No.</b>

837
00:49:02,006 --> 00:49:03,576
<b>I would not have thought
of this place.</b>

838
00:49:04,006 --> 00:49:05,076
<b>I like it.</b>

839
00:49:06,847 --> 00:49:08,246
<b>Let's get off now.</b>

840
00:49:09,217 --> 00:49:10,947
<b>Right. Hold on.</b>

841
00:49:11,947 --> 00:49:13,316
<b>Just in case.</b>

842
00:49:20,026 --> 00:49:21,397
<b>There.</b>

843
00:49:23,056 --> 00:49:24,066
<b>Let's go.</b>

844
00:49:54,296 --> 00:49:55,857
<b>The weather is great today.</b>

845
00:49:55,857 --> 00:49:56,857
<b>Right?</b>

846
00:49:58,326 --> 00:49:59,796
<b>Hey, it's them.</b>

847
00:49:59,796 --> 00:50:02,467
<b>- My goodness.
- Gosh.</b>

848
00:50:03,566 --> 00:50:05,867
<b>Isn't that Yeo Ha Jin?
Isn't that Anchor Lee Jeong Hoon?</b>

849
00:50:05,867 --> 00:50:07,437
<b>I don't believe this. No way!</b>

850
00:50:08,036 --> 00:50:09,336
<b>My goodness!</b>

851
00:50:10,236 --> 00:50:12,177
<b>- You guys look great together!
- You look great together!</b>

852
00:50:12,806 --> 00:50:13,806
<b>Let's go.</b>

853
00:50:14,276 --> 00:50:16,316
<b>That was quicker than I expected.</b>

854
00:50:16,847 --> 00:50:17,887
<b>Right.</b>

855
00:50:19,687 --> 00:50:22,857
<b>We should give up on this path.
Let's go back to the car.</b>

856
00:50:26,026 --> 00:50:27,927
<b>You said you really wanted
to walk this path.</b>

857
00:50:29,496 --> 00:50:31,427
<b>But people can recognize us.</b>

858
00:50:31,427 --> 00:50:32,766
<b>Let them, then.</b>

859
00:50:33,996 --> 00:50:35,667
<b>There's no reason why we must hide.</b>

860
00:50:42,177 --> 00:50:43,177
<b>Let's go.</b>

861
00:51:23,316 --> 00:51:25,117
<b>This is beautiful.</b>

862
00:51:25,717 --> 00:51:27,986
<b>This is how it feels
to see it up close.</b>

863
00:51:28,857 --> 00:51:30,717
<b>What do you say?
Isn't this worth it?</b>

864
00:51:31,556 --> 00:51:32,586
<b>It's nice.</b>

865
00:51:33,627 --> 00:51:35,996
<b>I only saw cherry blossoms
on the news every year.</b>

866
00:51:37,397 --> 00:51:39,697
<b>Let's come back and see
the cherry blossoms every spring.</b>

867
00:51:40,967 --> 00:51:41,967
<b>Yes.</b>

868
00:51:50,476 --> 00:51:51,877
<b>What are you thinking?</b>

869
00:51:53,207 --> 00:51:54,617
<b>That it's unfair.</b>

870
00:51:54,877 --> 00:51:56,377
<b>What's unfair?</b>

871
00:51:57,316 --> 00:51:58,647
<b>Come to think of it,</b>

872
00:51:59,246 --> 00:52:02,187
<b>I granted you
more than just one wish today.</b>

873
00:52:02,516 --> 00:52:04,486
<b>I had to try on
so many different outfits.</b>

874
00:52:05,586 --> 00:52:07,026
<b>Do you really think
it's that unfair?</b>

875
00:52:07,756 --> 00:52:09,857
<b>But sorry, it's too late.</b>

876
00:52:10,026 --> 00:52:11,427
<b>You can't take it back.</b>

877
00:52:11,996 --> 00:52:13,127
<b>Instead,</b>

878
00:52:14,127 --> 00:52:15,637
<b>grant me a wish too.</b>

879
00:52:17,167 --> 00:52:18,407
<b>That's so cheap.</b>

880
00:52:19,137 --> 00:52:20,637
<b>Fine, what is it?</b>

881
00:52:23,506 --> 00:52:25,306
<b>No matter what happens,</b>

882
00:52:26,677 --> 00:52:28,746
<b>don't ever say goodbye.</b>

883
00:52:31,447 --> 00:52:32,647
<b>That's my wish.</b>

884
00:52:37,627 --> 00:52:40,326
<b>I'll probably do it anyway
even if you didn't wish for that.</b>

885
00:52:43,296 --> 00:52:45,066
<b>Okay, then. I'll do that.</b>

886
00:52:50,296 --> 00:52:51,607
<b>You promised.</b>

887
00:52:53,566 --> 00:52:54,976
<b>Okay. I promise.</b>

888
00:53:52,467 --> 00:53:53,467
<b>Go inside.</b>

889
00:53:53,726 --> 00:53:56,167
<b>Okay. Call me when you get home.</b>

890
00:53:56,296 --> 00:53:58,836
<b>Okay. You should go in.</b>

891
00:54:02,177 --> 00:54:04,137
<b>Anchor Lee, give me your phone.</b>

892
00:54:04,137 --> 00:54:05,147
<b>My phone?</b>

893
00:54:06,207 --> 00:54:08,377
<b>- Why do you want my phone?
- It'll take only a second.</b>

894
00:54:21,226 --> 00:54:23,857
<b>You can't change that
without my permission, okay?</b>

895
00:54:24,197 --> 00:54:27,026
<b>Okay. Go in and get some rest.</b>

